INSERT INTO `calls` (`CallID`, `Date`, `Duration`, `Transcript`, `summary`, `category`) VALUES
(1, '2025-01-15', '06:32:00', 'Caller: Hi there, I recently purchased a blender from your site, but it\'s making this awful grinding noise after just a couple of uses. I\'m really disappointed because I was looking forward to making smoothies every morning. Agent: I\'m so sorry to hear about that issue with your blender. Could you please provide me with the order number so I can look into this for you? Caller: Sure, the order number is 45678. Do you think this is something that\'s covered under the warranty, or will I have to pay for repairs? Agent: Absolutely, this sounds like a manufacturing defect, so it\'s fully covered. Would you prefer a replacement or a refund? Also, do you still have the original packaging? Caller: I\'d love a replacement, please. Yes, I kept the box just in case. Thank you so much for helping me out with this. Agent: No problem at all. I\'ll process that replacement right away, and you should receive it within 3-5 business days.', 'Customer received a defective blender after only a couple of uses and is requesting a replacement.', 'Return / Refund'),
(2, '2025-02-20', '07:45:00', 'Caller: Hello, I was wondering if your webshop ships products to Canada, and if so, what are the shipping fees and estimated delivery times? I\'m interested in ordering some electronics. Agent: Yes, we do offer international shipping to Canada. The flat rate fee is $15, and it typically takes about 7-10 business days depending on customs. Caller: That sounds reasonable. Is there any way to track the package once it\'s shipped, and do you handle any customs duties? Agent: Definitely, you\'ll get a tracking number via email. As for customs, those are the responsibility of the customer, but we can provide invoices if needed. Caller: Alright, that\'s helpful. I think I\'ll go ahead and place the order now. Thanks for the information! Agent: You\'re welcome! If you run into any issues during checkout, feel free to call back.', 'The caller inquired about international shipping to Canada, including fees and estimated delivery times.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(3, '2025-03-10', '05:18:00', 'Caller: The pair of shoes I ordered arrived, but they\'re a size too small and pinching my toes. Can I exchange them for the next size up? Agent: Of course, we\'re happy to help with exchanges. What\'s your order ID, and what size would you like instead? Caller: The order ID is 98765, and I\'d like a size 9 instead of 8. Are they in stock right now? Agent: Let me check, yes, size 9 is available. I\'ll email you a return label, and the new pair will ship once we receive the old ones. Caller: Perfect, and how can I track the status of the new shipment? Thanks for making this easy.', 'The caller received a pair of shoes that is a size too small and is requesting an exchange for the next size up.', 'Return / Refund'),
(4, '2025-04-05', '08:10:00', 'Caller: Hi, I\'m shopping for wireless earbuds and need some recommendations for ones under $50 that have decent sound quality for everyday use like commuting and workouts. Agent: We have the SoundPro model priced at $45, which has excellent reviews for battery life and comfort during activities. Caller: Does it come with noise cancellation, or is that only on higher-end models? Also, are they sweat-resistant? Agent: No noise cancellation on this one, but it does have good passive isolation and is IPX4 sweat-resistant. Would you like me to add it to your cart? Caller: Yes, please do that. One more thing,  what\'s the return policy if they don\'t fit well? Agent: You have 30 days to return for a full refund. I\'ve added it; you can proceed to checkout now.', 'The caller is looking for wireless earbuds under $50 with good sound quality for everyday use, and asks about noise cancellation and sweat-resistance.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(5, '2025-05-22', '04:25:00', 'Caller: I see a pending charge on my credit card from your store, but I haven\'t received any order confirmation email yet. Is everything okay? Agent: Let me verify that for you. Do you have an order number or the email associated with the purchase? Caller: I don\'t have an order number, but my email is example@email.com. Agent: Thanks, it looks like the order processed successfully, and the confirmation should be in your inbox shortly, check spam if needed. Caller: Okay, I\'ll do that. Thanks for checking!', 'Caller has a pending charge on their credit card but no order confirmation email.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(6, '2025-06-18', '09:05:00', 'Caller: Hello, I\'d like to have my order gift-wrapped with a personal note inside. Is that something you can do, and how much extra does it cost? Agent: Yes, we offer gift wrapping for an additional $5. What would you like the note to say? Caller: Please write \"Happy Birthday, with love from Mom.\" Also, is there an option for express shipping to make sure it arrives on time? Agent: Got the note. Express shipping is available for $10 more, which cuts delivery to 2-3 days. Caller: Let\'s add both, please. The order number is 33445 if that helps. Agent: All set, wrapping and express added. It should arrive by the date you need. Anything else today?', 'A customer wants to add gift wrapping with a personal note and expedited shipping to their existing order.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(7, '2025-07-09', '06:40:00', 'Caller: I just received the book I ordered, but several pages are missing, and the binding seems loose. This is really frustrating as it was a gift. Agent: I\'m truly sorry for the poor quality. Can you give me the order details so I can arrange a resolution? Caller: Order number 11223. I\'d prefer a full refund rather than a replacement, if possible. Agent: Understood. Do you want to return it, or can we just process the refund since it\'s defective? Caller: I\'d like to return it, please send a label. How long will the refund take once you receive it? Agent: Label emailed. Refund should post within 5-7 business days after receipt.', 'Caller received a defective book with missing pages and loose binding, requesting a full refund or return.', 'Return / Refund'),
(8, '2025-08-14', '07:15:00', 'Caller: Hi, I noticed the same product is cheaper on Amazon. Do you guys offer price matching to keep things competitive? Agent: We do price match within 7 days of purchase if you provide a link to the competitor\'s listing. Caller: Great, here\'s the link: amazon.com/product. It\'s $10 less there. Agent: Let me verify, yes, it qualifies. I\'ll adjust your order and refund the difference. Caller: Awesome, that saves me some money. Thanks for being flexible about this.', 'Caller inquired about price matching with a competitor\'s listing and received assistance from the agent.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(9, '2025-09-25', '05:30:00', 'Caller: My promotional code isn\'t working on the sale items in my cart. Is there a restriction I\'m missing? Agent: Some codes exclude sale items. Which code are you trying to use? Caller: It\'s WELCOME10. Maybe there\'s another one I can use instead? Agent: That one is for full-price only. Try NEWUSER15, which should work on everything. Caller: It applied! Thanks for the tip.', 'The caller had trouble applying a promotional code to sale items in their cart.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(10, '2025-10-30', '08:20:00', 'Caller: Hello, I need to update the payment method on my account because my old card expired. Agent: No problem. Are you logged in, or do you have a specific order number? Caller: Order 33445. I want to switch to a new Visa card. Agent: I\'ve updated it. Can you confirm if the new charge goes through correctly? Caller: Yes, it looks good now. Just to be sure, will this apply to future subscriptions too? Agent: Absolutely, it\'s updated across your account.', 'The caller needed to update their payment method on their account due to an expired card and successfully switched to a new Visa card.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(11, '2024-11-03', '06:50:00', 'Caller: The laptop charger I bought doesn\'t fit my HP model at all, it\'s for Dell, I think. This is a mix-up. Agent: Apologies for the error. What\'s the order ID so I can correct this? Caller: 55667. I need the right one ASAP as my battery is dying. Agent: We\'ll rush a replacement. Expect it in 2 days with expedited shipping at no cost. Caller: That\'s a relief. Thanks for handling it quickly.', 'The caller received an incorrect laptop charger and needs a replacement, especially since their battery is dying.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(12, '2024-12-18', '07:35:00', 'Caller: Hi, can I get a discount if I bundle a shirt and pants together? I\'m shopping for work clothes. Agent: Yes, we have bundle deals, 10% off for matching sets like that. Caller: Sounds good. Can you help add them to my cart? The navy shirt and black pants. Agent: Added, and the discount applied automatically. Ready to check out? Caller: Yes, thanks. One more, do you have sizing guides? Agent: Absolutely, check the product pages or I can email them.', 'Caller asked about bundling a shirt and pants for work clothes, received information on discounts and had items added to cart. Also inquired about sizing guides.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(13, '2024-01-07', '05:45:00', 'Caller: My delivery was left at the wrong house down the street. Luckily, the neighbor brought it over, but this could have been bad. Agent: We\'re sorry for the mix-up with the carrier. Was everything intact? Caller: Yes, but I\'d like a refund on the shipping fee as compensation. Agent: Fair enough, I\'ve credited it back to your account. Caller: Appreciate that. Please note the correct address for future orders.', 'The caller\'s delivery was left at the wrong house and was fortunately brought over by a neighbor, but they are seeking a refund on the shipping fee as compensation.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(14, '2024-02-21', '09:10:00', 'Caller: Hello, I\'m curious if your products are eco-friendly. Specifically, the clothing line,  what materials do you use? Agent: Our clothing is made from recycled fabrics and organic cotton, with certifications for sustainability. Caller: That\'s impressive. Do you have any third-party verifications I can look up? Agent: Yes, we\'re GOTS certified. I can send links if you\'d like. Caller: Please do. I\'m going to buy a couple of shirts now. Thanks! Agent: Email sent. Happy shopping!', 'The caller inquired about the eco-friendliness and sustainability of the clothing line, specifically asking about materials and certifications.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(15, '2024-03-14', '04:55:00', 'Caller: I can\'t seem to find my wish list on the site anymore. It was there yesterday. Agent: Are you logged into the correct account? Sometimes they get hidden. Caller: Yes, but it\'s empty now. Can you restore it? Agent: Let me check our backup, yes, I\'ve restored it for you. Caller: Phew, thanks a lot.', 'Caller is unable to access their wish list and needs assistance restoring it.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(16, '2024-04-29', '08:00:00', 'Caller: The color of the sweater I received is way off from the photo online, it\'s more brown than beige. Agent: Colors can vary due to screen settings, but if it\'s not what you expected, we can arrange a return. Caller: Yes, please. Order 77889. Will I get free return shipping? Agent: Absolutely, label on the way. Would you like a different color as replacement? Caller: No, just a refund. Thanks for understanding.', 'The caller received a sweater with an incorrect color, requesting a return and refund.', 'Return / Refund'),
(17, '2024-05-11', '06:20:00', 'Caller: Hi, do you provide installation services for large appliances like refrigerators? Agent: We do for an additional fee of $50, including haul-away of the old one. Caller: Perfect for my new fridge order. Can you schedule it? Agent: Sure, what date works? Let\'s say next Tuesday. Caller: Tuesday is good. Confirm the address? Agent: All set. See you then.', 'The caller inquired about installation services for a refrigerator and scheduled an appointment for next Tuesday.', 'Service Request'),
(18, '2024-06-26', '07:25:00', 'Caller: My coupon code expired yesterday, but I just found out about it. Can you make an exception and honor it? Agent: As a one-time courtesy, yes. What\'s the code? Caller: SUMMER20. It\'s for 20% off. Agent: Applied to your cart. Proceed when ready. Caller: You\'re a lifesaver. Thanks!', 'Caller requested an exception to honor an expired coupon code, which was granted as a one-time courtesy.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(19, '2024-07-09', '05:40:00', 'Caller: Hello, could you help me track my package? I have the order number. Agent: Sure, what\'s the number? Caller: 99001. It was supposed to arrive yesterday. Agent: It shows out for delivery today. Should be there by evening. Caller: Okay, I\'ll keep an eye out. Thanks.', 'Caller is trying to track their package that was supposed to arrive yesterday.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(20, '2024-08-24', '08:15:00', 'Caller: The item I ordered is now out of stock, but my order went through. What\'s going on? Agent: It\'s on backorder, expected in 2 weeks. Or we can cancel if you prefer. Caller: I\'d rather cancel and get a refund, please. Agent: Refund processed. Sorry for the delay. Caller: No worries, thanks for the quick fix. Agent: Let me know if you need alternatives.', 'The caller\'s order went through but is now out of stock, with an option to cancel and receive a refund or wait two weeks for delivery.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(21, '2024-09-16', '06:30:00', 'Caller: Hi, I need some help understanding your size chart for jeans. The measurements are confusing. Agent: For jeans, measure your waist and inseam. Which style are you looking at? Caller: The slim fit ones. My waist is 32 inches. Agent: That would be size 32. Inseam options are 30 or 32. Caller: I\'ll take 32/32. Thanks for clarifying.', 'The caller needed help understanding the size chart for slim fit jeans and was having trouble with the measurements.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(22, '2024-10-31', '07:10:00', 'Caller: My product review isn\'t showing up on the site even after a few days. Agent: Reviews go through moderation, but it shouldn\'t take long. Let me check. Caller: It\'s been over a week now. Agent: Found it, approved now. It should appear shortly. Caller: Great, I appreciate the feedback system. Thanks.', 'The caller had an issue with their product review not being displayed on the site despite waiting several days, and the agent helped to resolve the issue by checking and approving it.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(23, '2024-11-13', '05:05:00', 'Caller: Hello, does your store have a loyalty program for frequent shoppers? Agent: Yes, you earn points on every purchase, redeemable for discounts. Caller: How do I sign up, and what are the benefits? Agent: Just create an account on our site. Benefits include exclusive sales too. Caller: Signed up! Thanks for the info.', 'The caller inquired about your store\'s loyalty program, including how to sign up and benefits', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(24, '2024-12-28', '09:20:00', 'Caller: The battery life on this watch is much shorter than what was advertised, only lasting a few hours. Agent: That doesn\'t sound right. Have you tried optimizing settings like turning off notifications? Caller: Yes, I did all that. Still drains fast. Agent: Let\'s return it for inspection. I\'ll send a label. Caller: Okay, hope the next one is better. Thanks. Agent: We\'ll make sure. Refund if needed.', 'The caller reported a shorter battery life on their watch than advertised, despite optimizing settings.', 'Return / Refund'),
(25, '2023-01-10', '04:50:00', 'Caller: Hi, can I use PayPal as a payment method on your checkout page? Agent: Yes, it\'s available at checkout. Caller: It\'s not showing up for me. What could be wrong? Agent: Try refreshing the page or clearing your cache. Caller: That worked. Thanks!', 'The caller had trouble seeing PayPal as a payment option on checkout, but was able to resolve the issue by refreshing the page and clearing their cache.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(26, '2023-02-25', '08:30:00', 'Caller: My order is delayed, and I need it soon. Why is it taking so long? Agent: Due to recent weather disruptions in shipping routes. New ETA is next week. Caller: That\'s inconvenient. Can you compensate with free shipping on my next order? Agent: Absolutely, I\'ve added a credit to your account. Caller: Much better. Thanks for understanding.', 'The caller\'s order was delayed due to weather disruptions in shipping routes, but the agent offered a solution by adding a credit for free shipping on their next order.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(27, '2023-03-19', '06:15:00', 'Caller: Hello, is there any recall information on the toy set I bought last month? Agent: Let me check, which specific set? Caller: The building blocks for kids aged 3-5. Agent: No recalls on that one. It\'s safe. Caller: Good to hear. Thanks for confirming.', 'The caller inquired about recall information on a toy set purchased last month and was assured it is safe with no recalls.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(28, '2023-04-04', '07:40:00', 'Caller: I\'m not receiving your promotional newsletters anymore, even though I\'m subscribed. Agent: Have you checked your spam folder? Sometimes they end up there. Caller: Yes, nothing. Can you resubscribe me or update? Agent: Let\'s update your preferences. Should start coming again. Caller: Fixed now. Appreciate it. Agent: Glad to help.', 'Caller is not receiving promotional newsletters despite being subscribed and wants to be resubscribed or updated.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(29, '2023-05-29', '05:35:00', 'Caller: Hi, do you offer discounts for bulk orders, like 20 custom shirts for an event? Agent: For orders over 10, we give 15% off. Caller: Excellent. How do I apply that? Agent: Add to cart, and it\'ll apply at checkout. Caller: All set. Thanks!', 'The caller inquired about bulk order discounts for a custom shirt event.', ''),
(30, '2023-06-11', '08:05:00', 'Caller: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to view my shopping cart. Agent: Sorry about that. Have you updated to the latest version? Caller: Yes, still happening. Agent: Try reinstalling. Meanwhile, use the website. Caller: Reinstall worked. Thanks for the suggestion. Agent: Update with fixes coming soon.', 'The caller experienced issues with their mobile app crashing when viewing their shopping cart, but was able to resolve the issue by reinstalling.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(31, '2023-07-26', '06:25:00', 'Caller: Hello, are there vegan options in your skincare products? I\'m looking for something gentle. Agent: Many are vegan, look for the label. I recommend the aloe-based cream. Caller: Does it have any animal testing? Agent: No, we\'re cruelty-free. Caller: Adding it now. Thanks!', 'The caller asked about vegan options in skincare products and was recommended an aloe-based cream that is both vegan and cruelty-free.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(32, '2023-08-08', '07:50:00', 'Caller: My package was stolen from the porch. What can I do about it? Agent: That\'s awful. We can file a claim with the carrier. Caller: How does that process work? Will I get a replacement? Agent: Fill out the online form, and we\'ll resend or refund once approved. Caller: I\'ll do that. Thanks for guiding me.', 'A customer\'s package was stolen from their porch and they\'re seeking assistance with filing a claim to get a replacement.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(33, '2023-09-23', '05:10:00', 'Caller: Hi, I need to change the email address linked to my account. Agent: Sure, first verify the old email by entering a code we\'ll send. Caller: Code received and entered. Agent: Updated to the new one. Caller: Quick and easy. Thanks.', 'Caller requested to update their account\'s linked email address.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(34, '2023-10-15', '09:15:00', 'Caller: These wired headphones have terrible static noise right out of the box. Agent: That sounds defective. Have you tried a different device? Caller: Yes, same issue. Agent: We\'ll replace them. Send back the old pair? Caller: Yes, please provide a label. Agent: On its way. New ones shipping today.', 'Caller experiencing static noise with new headphones and requested replacement.', 'Return / Refund'),
(35, '2023-11-30', '04:45:00', 'Caller: Hello, do you extend return periods during the holidays? Agent: Yes, purchases from now until December can be returned by January 15. Caller: That\'s convenient for gifts. Agent: Shop with peace of mind. Caller: Will do. Thanks!', 'The caller inquired about extending the return period during the holiday season.', 'Return / Refund'),
(36, '2023-12-12', '08:00:00', 'Caller: My order arrived with extra items I didn\'t purchase. What should I do? Agent: That\'s our mistake, feel free to keep them as a gift. Caller: Really? That\'s generous. Agent: Yes, enjoy the extras. Caller: Wow, thanks a lot!', 'The caller received an order with extra items they didn\'t purchase and the agent offered to let them keep the extras as a gift.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(37, '2025-01-27', '06:35:00', 'Caller: Hi, does your website have accessibility features for visually impaired users? Agent: Yes, it\'s compatible with screen readers, and we have alt text on all images. Caller: Great, that\'s important to me. Agent: If you need more help, let us know. Caller: Will do. Thanks.', 'The caller asked about accessibility features for visually impaired users on our website.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(38, '2025-02-09', '07:45:00', 'Caller: The material on this dress is causing irritation on my skin, it\'s itchy. Agent: Sorry to hear that. Perhaps an allergic reaction. Want to return? Caller: Yes, order 22334. Agent: Refund starting now. Send it back. Caller: Thanks for the hassle-free process.', 'The caller experienced skin irritation from the dress material and would like to return the order.', 'Return / Refund'),
(39, '2025-03-24', '05:20:00', 'Caller: Hello, how can I check the balance on my gift card? Agent: Provide the code, and I\'ll look it up. Caller: It\'s ABC123. Agent: You have $50 remaining. Caller: Perfect, thanks.', 'The caller wanted to check the balance on their gift card, provided the code (ABC123), and was informed by the agent that they had $50 remaining.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(40, '2025-04-06', '08:10:00', 'Caller: I need the assembly instructions for the desk I bought, they weren\'t in the box. Agent: No problem. I can email a PDF version. Caller: Yes, please. My email is deskbuyer@email.com. Agent: Sent. If you have questions during assembly, call back. Caller: Received it. Thanks so much!', 'Caller needed assembly instructions for their purchased desk and agent emailed a PDF version.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(41, '2025-05-21', '06:50:00', 'Caller: Hi, can I return an item without the original receipt? I lost it. Agent: We can issue store credit if you have the order number or email. Caller: It\'s an online purchase, order 44556. Agent: Found it. Return approved for credit. Caller: That\'s fine. Thanks.', 'The caller wanted to return an item without the original receipt, but was able to get approval for store credit with their order number.', 'Return / Refund'),
(42, '2025-06-03', '07:15:00', 'Caller: The digital game code you sent isn\'t redeeming properly on the platform. Agent: Let\'s troubleshoot. Which platform? Caller: Steam. Agent: I\'ll resend a new code, try that. Caller: It worked this time. Appreciate the quick help.', 'The caller had issues with redeeming a digital game code on Steam and the agent helped troubleshoot and resolved the issue by resending a new code.', 'Service Request'),
(43, '2025-07-18', '05:05:00', 'Caller: Hello, do you carry pet-friendly cleaning products that won\'t harm my dog? Agent: Yes, our non-toxic line is safe for pets. Caller: Specifically for floors? Agent: Absolutely, the floor cleaner is pet-safe. Caller: I\'ll order some. Thanks!', 'Customer inquired about pet-friendly cleaning products, specifically for floors, and placed an order.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(44, '2025-08-30', '09:25:00', 'Caller: My subscription renewed without warning, and I wanted to cancel it. Agent: Subscriptions auto-renew, but I can turn that off and issue a refund. Caller: Please do both. Agent: Done, refund for this cycle processed. Caller: Thanks for fixing it promptly.', 'Caller\'s subscription renewed unexpectedly and they wanted to cancel it and receive a refund.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(45, '2025-09-12', '04:45:00', 'Caller: Hi, can you compare two phone models for me? Battery life is key. Agent: Model A has 12 hours, B has 8. Caller: What about camera quality? Agent: A is better there too. Caller: I\'ll go with A.', 'The caller compared battery life and camera quality of two phone models.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(46, '2025-10-27', '08:15:00', 'Caller: The paint sample I got doesn\'t match the color on your site at all. Agent: Samples can vary slightly, but if it\'s way off, return it. Caller: Yes, it\'s not close. Agent: Send it back; we\'ll ship a new one free. Caller: Thanks. Hope the next is accurate.', 'The caller received a paint sample that didn\'t match the color on our website and wants to return it.', 'Return / Refund'),
(47, '2024-11-09', '06:30:00', 'Caller: Hello, can I extend the warranty on my electronics purchase? Agent: Yes, for $20 per year on most items. Caller: For the TV I bought. Agent: Added, now covered for 3 years. Caller: Great, peace of mind.', 'Caller requested to extend the warranty on their electronics purchase', 'Service Request'),
(48, '2024-12-24', '07:45:00', 'Caller: My package arrived soaked from rain, but thankfully nothing damaged. Agent: Glad it\'s okay. We\'ll improve weather-proofing. Caller: Good to know for future. Agent: Noted on your account. Caller: Thanks anyway.', 'The caller reported that their package arrived soaked from rain, but fortunately the contents were not damaged.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(49, '2024-01-16', '05:15:00', 'Caller: Hi, how do I unsubscribe from your email list? Too many coming in. Agent: Click the link at the bottom, or I can do it. Caller: Please handle it for me. Agent: You\'re unsubscribed. Caller: Much better. Thanks.', 'The caller requested assistance with unsubscribing from the email list due to receiving too many emails.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(50, '2024-02-01', '08:35:00', 'Caller: The toy I ordered is missing some pieces, my kid is upset. Agent: Sorry! Send a photo of what\'s missing? Caller: Emailing now. Agent: Parts on the way, no charge. Caller: Thanks, that\'ll make his day.', 'The caller reported that their toy was missing some pieces and was upset about it. The agent apologized, offered to send replacement parts at no additional cost, and confirmed receipt of a photo from the caller.', 'Return / Refund'),
(51, '2024-03-18', '06:10:00', 'Caller: Hello, do you have a student discount program? Agent: 10% off with valid ID. Caller: How do I apply it online? Agent: Upload ID at checkout. Caller: Easy enough. Thanks!', 'The caller inquired about the student discount program and how to apply it online.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(52, '2024-04-02', '07:30:00', 'Caller: My loyalty points aren\'t updating after my last purchase. Agent: It can take 48 hours. Let me check. Caller: It\'s been longer. Agent: Manually added now. Caller: Appreciate the fix.', 'The caller reported an issue with their loyalty points not updating after a recent purchase, but was assisted by the agent who manually added the points.', 'Account / Data Issue'),
(53, '2024-05-17', '05:25:00', 'Caller: Hi, are there eco-friendly shipping options available? Agent: We offer carbon-neutral shipping at no extra cost. Caller: Does it slow down delivery? Agent: No, same speed. Caller: Select that for my order.', 'The caller inquired about eco-friendly shipping options and was informed that they offer carbon-neutral shipping at no extra cost.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(54, '2024-06-29', '09:00:00', 'Caller: The software I downloaded won\'t install on my computer. Agent: Is your OS compatible? Windows or Mac? Caller: Windows 10. Agent: Run as administrator. Caller: That did it. Thanks! Agent: Glad it worked.', 'The caller experienced an issue installing software and was able to resolve the problem by running the installation as an administrator.', 'Service Request'),
(55, '2024-07-11', '04:40:00', 'Caller: Hello, can I return an item that\'s been opened but unused? Agent: Yes, as long as it\'s in original condition. Caller: It\'s a shirt I tried on once. Agent: That\'s fine. Send label? Caller: Yes, please.', 'The caller wants to return an open-but-unused item (a shirt) and is asking for a return label.', 'Return / Refund'),
(56, '2024-08-26', '08:05:00', 'Caller: My order is stuck in \"processing\" for days now. Agent: Let me see, payment cleared? Caller: Yes, card was charged. Agent: Approved manually. Shipping soon. Caller: Finally, thanks.', 'Order is delayed and the caller is concerned about the status.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(57, '2024-09-08', '06:25:00', 'Caller: Hi, do your food products have allergy information? Agent: Yes, detailed on labels and site. Caller: Any with nuts? Agent: This snack is nut-free. Caller: I\'ll take it.', 'Caller inquired about allergy information for food products, specifically looking for nut-free options.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(58, '2024-10-23', '07:15:00', 'Caller: The picture frame arrived bent out of shape. Agent: Likely shipping damage. Photo please? Caller: Sent. Agent: Replacement coming. Caller: Thanks for the swift action.', 'The caller reported that their picture frame arrived damaged, which was likely caused by shipping issues.', 'Return / Refund'),
(59, '2024-11-05', '05:35:00', 'Caller: Hello, is there a virtual try-on feature for glasses? Agent: Yes, via our app. Caller: How do I access it? Agent: Download and upload photo. Caller: Sounds fun. Thanks!', 'The caller inquired about the virtual try-on feature for glasses and was provided with instructions on how to access it.', 'Product Inquiry'),
(60, '2024-12-20', '08:40:00', 'Caller: My referral code isn\'t applying for my friend. Agent: Has it expired? Caller: It\'s new. Agent: Fixed on our end. Caller: Try again, works! Thanks.', 'The caller had an issue with their referral code not applying to a friend\'s purchase, but it was resolved when they tried again.', 'Shipping Issue'),
(61, '2023-01-02', '06:00:00', 'Caller: Hi, can I customize a product like engraving on a mug? Agent: Yes, for $5 extra. Caller: What font options? Agent: Several, script or block. Caller: Script please. Add it.', 'The caller inquired about customizing a product with engraving and font options.', 'Product Inquiry'),
